{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2a04907a86","title":"毛泽东等祝贺勃列日湿夫和柯西金任职的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"841f93abb1","index":0,"year":1964,"month":10,"day":16,"articleId":"2a04907a86"}],"tags":[{"id":"29143cbd32","name":"无产阶级国际主义","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"48bc2988a4","type":"title","text":"毛泽东等祝贺勃列日湿夫和柯西金任职的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"7e2b19799b","type":"paragraph","text":"莫斯科苏联共产党中央委员会第一书记列·伊·勃列日湿夫同志，苏联最高苏维埃主席团主席阿·伊·米高扬同志，苏联部长会议主席阿·尼·柯西金同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"544f1d9b6b","type":"paragraph","text":"得悉勃列日湿夫同志当选为苏共中央第一书记，柯西金同志被任命为部长会议主席，我们代表中国人民、中国共产党和中国政府，向你们表示热烈的祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"8008377ba3","type":"paragraph","text":"我们表心地希望，兄弟的苏联人民，在苏联共产党和苏联政府的领导下，在今后各方面的建设工作中和维护世界和平的斗争中，取得新的成就。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"ea2d5aa446","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党、中国政府和中国人民对于伟大的苏联、苏联共产竞和苏联人民在前进道路上的每一个进展，都是高兴的。最近苏联“上升”号宇宙飞船的成功发射和顺利着陆，是苏联劳动人民的又一项伟大成就。我们愿意借此机会向你们，并且通过你们，向伟大的苏联人民，表示夷心的庆贺。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"aa171bcbd9","type":"paragraph","text":"中苏两党、两国在马克思列宁主义和无产阶级国际主义的基础上团结起来！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"d18cdab82f","type":"paragraph","text":"祝中苏两国人民兑弟的牢不可破的友谊不断发展！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"c37c068db0","type":"paragraph","text":"祝中苏两国人民在反对以美国为首的帝国主义、保卫世界和平的共同斗争中不断取得胜利！","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"4715b894f0","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"e9d8c1d0af","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"9c69bdf3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国主席毛泽东","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"d23b8eb4d8","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"ab067c3d6a","type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民代表大会","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"ef3a4c6643","type":"paragraph","text":"常务委员会委员长朱德","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"aec3d162ae","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国国务院总理周恩来","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"},{"id":"a785cc962d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年十月十六日于北京","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86"}],"page":{"id":"462199d528","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"2a04907a86","start":201,"end":202}}}},"__N_SSG":true}